<heading bold="true" box="[189,310,541,567]" fontSize="11" level="2" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" reason="2">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,310,541,567]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[189,1399,588,651]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<taxonomicName authority="Lars Hedenäs, 2017" authorityName="Lars Hedenäs" authorityYear="2017" box="[189,494,588,614]" class="Bryopsida" family="Dicranaceae" genus="Oncophorus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dicranales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="integerrimus" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[189,494,588,614]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Oncophorus integerrimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[504,598,589,615]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differs from 
<taxonomicName authority="(Hedw.) Brid." authorityName="(Hedw.) Brid." box="[759,1044,588,615]" class="Bryopsida" family="Dicranaceae" genus="Cynodontium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dicranales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="virens">
<emphasis box="[759,869,589,615]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">O. virens</emphasis>
(Hedw.) Brid.
</taxonomicName>
by its more loosely incurved leaves when dry, and in having entire or almost entire upper leaf margins.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[189,954,690,763]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="25.[189,324,690,716]" box="[189,324,690,716]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,324,690,716]" fontSize="11" level="2" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" reason="2">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,324,690,716]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[189,954,737,763]" box="[189,954,737,763]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
The epithet ‘ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lars Hedenäs" authorityYear="2017" box="[339,489,738,763]" class="Bryopsida" family="Dicranaceae" genus="Oncophorus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dicranales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="integerrimus">
<emphasis box="[339,489,738,763]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">integerrimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ refers to the mostly entire leaf margin.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
